 <H1>Strict 2PL</H1> 
 <P><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Strict 2PL:
</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>If T wants to read an object, first obtains an S lock.
<LI>If T wants to modify an object, first obtains X lock.
<LI>Hold all locks until end of transaction.
</UL></UL><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Guarantees serializability, and recoverable schedule, too!
</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>also avoids WW problems!</UL></UL></P>

